## Rainbow Bridge

The Rainbow Bridge is a bridge between Ethereum and NEAR. It allows Ethereum contracts to call NEAR functions and vice versa.

### Rainbow Bridge Contract

The Rainbow Bridge contract is deployed to `rainbow.near`.

